| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1301 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7967fb39-01b6-5af5-bcb3-7fcdf7b961e6"
